13
00:02:57,844 --> 00:02:59,053
Rozkaz.

14
00:02:59,262 --> 00:03:04,559
To nie! Lord Faust, ozaj máme
poslúchať niekoho iného?

15
00:03:04,601 --> 00:03:07,770
